microprocessor_definition.name: Delta calculator
microprocessor_definition.description: Microcontroller to calculate delta of a given number

node.label: Number
node.description: The input signal to be processed.

node.label: Delta
node.description: The input signal to be processed.

object.script:
tickTime = 0 lastValue = 0 function onTick() value = input.getNumber(1)
tickTime = tickTime + 1 if (tickTime >= 60) then tickTime = 0
delta = value - lastValue lastValue = value end
output.setNumber(1, delta) end
